metadata.name: 2011 WOO Sprint Car #1
metadata.description: In 2011, Tony Stewart showcased his greatness and versatility again - proving to be a once in generation driver. At Ohsweken Speedway (Ontario, Canada) in July 2011, Stewart captured his first career World of Outlaws Sprint Car Series (WOO) victory. While Stewart had won three championships as a WOO owner, it wasnâ€™t until July 27, 2011 that Stewart celebrated in victory lane as a WOO driver and fulfilled a lifelong dream.
